Load cbb player box score stats

load_player_box_scores.Rd

Pull in statistics aggregated by player and game for a given season.

Usage

load_player_box_scores(seasons = most_recent_season())

Arguments

seasons

an integer of seasons to fetch data for. Defaults to the most recent season. Pass in TRUE to fetch all seasons.

Value

a dataframe of player box scores.

Examples

# \donttest{
load_player_box_scores()
